{"id": 3021, "genre": 1000, "title": "最近几年，你都为哪些「孤独消费」买过单？", "description": "产生这些消费不一定是因为孤独，但它们确实让一个人的生活变得更自在了点。（题图来自：iStock ©️ nuvolanevicata）", "record_count": 9009, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191001010939WMYpRNiqGvLKx2Or.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-02T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5944, "title": "最近几年，你都为哪些「孤独消费」买过单？", "content": "最近几年，你都为哪些「孤独消费」买过单？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 347572, "content": "一人食餐厅/一人小火锅，不用凑很多人也能去吃", "image": "img/option/option/20190930194412hfitm21CP4LFpv9B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347580, "content": "一人旅行/胶囊酒店，玩和住都不需要找同伴", "image": "img/option/option/20190930212805iySI4ldrj2vHRQmx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347582, "content": "可以对话的智能小家电，能帮忙干活儿还能唠嗑", "image": "img/option/option/20190930213351kUKQzYmBJprdoWV6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347583, "content": "迷你 KTV，一个人就能唱，还不担心别人听见", "image": "img/option/option/20191001004933QHfCIYEJelivsumB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347584, "content": "迷你微波炉、迷你冰箱之类适合独居的小型家电", "image": "img/option/option/20191001004941rmzsvVZd1pK2ukLx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347587, "content": "微型自助健身房，免去了运动时的 peer pressure", "image": "img/option/option/20190930232455FEUj36ySdcxVHouq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347591, "content": "社交/聊天 app，未必要做朋友，但也会跟别人聊几句", "image": "img/option/option/20191001001628cExof3OZbYdShsQa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347592, "content": "游戏/手办/宠物等等，同时具有“陪伴+解闷”双重功能", "image": "img/option/option/20191001003214nAa0UlZz9DM3vGTx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 347593, "content": "都没有，我不太需要/我有其他的消费选择", "image": "img/option/option/201910010034378o2p90DGrbv5Znml.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}